headline: What You Need to Know Ahead of Hilton’s Earnings Release
summary: Hilton is poised to report its fiscal fourth-quarter results in the near future, and analysts are projecting double-digit growth in earnings, reflecting strong operating momentum and sustained demand across its global hotel portfolio.
